  "body": "### Description\n\nCustom OAuth2 implementations may return an absolute time value in `expires_in`, as opposed to a relative duration - `OidcClient` can not detect the access token has expired in such cases\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nAdd a configuration property and use the `expires_in` as is as opposed to adding it to current/issued at time when checking if the token has expired",
